# Document binaries: ignored by default so a stray or sensitive TEST document is
# never accidentally committed (e.g. by `git add -A`). Put unvetted test inputs
# in sandbox/ or exports/ (both ignored). Only the curated areas below may hold
# committed documents — reference fixtures, samples, and self-contained template
# bases (source.hwpx). To commit a document elsewhere on purpose, use `git add -f`.
*.hwp
*.hwpx
*.docx
*.pptx
*.pdf
!references/**
!samples/**
!skills/templates/**
